OMG!!!!!  My girlfriend and I has ordered from here 3x, and each time we were pleasantly satisfied with our order. Now if you've read my other pizza review, you would know that I absolutely love pizza and I was addicted to one location in which I had to leave the borough to go and get pizza from that place... BUT not anymore, Angela's pizzeria is a God sent gem in the neighborhood OMFG!!!!! lol... listen the grandma pie is to die for and I'm not playing, when we start eating we can't stop literally...lol its so fresh and tasty, its light and airy and its not too much crust with just the right amount of sauce that you enjoy every bite, even my grand daughter at the age of 3 has said "this is so delicious pop pop" and she's a very picky eater but to sum it all up I highly recommend Angela's pizzeria to anyone whos addicted to pizza like I am and you must have the grandma pie!!!!
